MfKpwVwDcfosrtLRicYxaA">Thạch Cự các - 石柜閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Thu%E1%BB%B7-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-qu%C3%A1n-th%E1%BB%A7/poem-1FwX65prJsA05uboQgeyRg">Thuỷ thượng quán thủ - 水上盥手</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/%C6%AFu-l%C3%A3o/poem-qIyjHbe0mdIhfT_8koDJGA">Ưu lão - 憂老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-10/poem-CK3p3IGh3Pd8_HG2ZRIcWw">Xuân nhật tuyệt cú thập thủ kỳ 10 - 春日絕句十首其十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br></div>	</div>
